						               													<description>&amp;ldquo;We&amp;rsquo;re very afraid to enter! The castle of the Colorsnatching Witch is frightening!&amp;#10;The evil witch had attempted stealing the rainbow before and leaving the world colorless &amp;ndash; and she hadn&amp;rsquo;t managed to... until now!&amp;#10;The Kanyitos are trapped inside the castle, and can&amp;rsquo;t help humankind anymore. Marahuero, the witch&amp;rsquo;s cat, helped us get in and told us how to save them. Now it&amp;rsquo;s too late to turn back. We have only three days to rescue them and get away!&amp;rdquo;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Kanyimajo is a card game in which you&amp;rsquo;ll be trying to free the Kanyitos and Kanyikats from the claws of the evil Coloursnatching Witch (Bruja Robacolores).&amp;#10;You&amp;rsquo;ll have to collect kokeshi-doll amulets, jewels and flowers of many colours to break the witch&amp;rsquo;s spell, and confide with the Amaterasu and Izanami to break free.&amp;#10;Only the boldest may manage to win the game &amp;ndash; that is, if they don&amp;rsquo;t come across the evil witch thrice!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the Kanyito universe, Kanyitos are creatures which control feelings through the use of color.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The evil Coloursnatching Witch, Kuroi Majo, has decided to kidnap them to make the world devoid of color and positive feelings. Marahuero, the witch&amp;rsquo;s cat, has decided to aid you in rescuing them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To set a Kanyito free, you&amp;rsquo;ll need to find amongst the cards an amulet, a flower and a Kanyito of the same color.&amp;#10;Some of the Kanyitos have been transformed into Kanyikats, Kanyito cats, for which you&amp;rsquo;ll have to find a jewel and a kokeshi-doll instead.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The evil Witch will be chasing you, hidden in the deck. If you come across her three times, she&amp;rsquo;ll banish you from the castle!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
